Package hms.appointment

Class AppointmentOutcome

java.lang.Object
hms.appointment.AppointmentOutcome
public class AppointmentOutcome extends Object
Represents the outcome of a medical appointment, detailing the diagnosis, medication prescribed, and consultation notes. Also includes a resolved status to indicate whether the appointment's concerns were resolved.
